item.title: Our new release apps this month
item.description: Tired of typing online check-in information over and over again , save your information once and simply copy and paste it from our app for your whole family MyPass-MyID Passport scanner, driving license scanner, ID scanner. Fill out your online check-in quickly by copy and paste your info from the app. Safe to leave your passport in hotel and show the scanned image from the app when you are requested to do so.
